        Queensland First Home Owner Grant: What Brisbane Sellers Need to Know About FHOG Buyers
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        The Queensland FHOG does not apply to established homes. Understanding which incentives actually affect the buyer pool for your property will help you set a more accurate price and anticipate buyer behaviour.
      </p>
    </div>
